Package com.olegtoropoff.petcareappointment.dto

Class AppointmentDto

java.lang.Object
com.olegtoropoff.petcareappointment.dto.AppointmentDto
public class AppointmentDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for representing appointment details. This class encapsulates the information related to an appointment, including its date, time, participants, status, and associated pets.
